Step 2 : Add a URL Route
from django.urls import path
from django.views.generic import TemplateView

urlpatterns = [
    path('team/', TemplateView.as_view(template_name='our_team.html'), name='our_team'),
]


Step 3 : Add alink to the footer 
<a href="{% url 'our_team' %}" style="color: #fff; margin: 0 10px;">Or Team</a>




